identity.Description: The identity of the connected cluster.

properties.Description: Describes the connected cluster resource properties.

systemData.Description: Metadata pertaining to creation and last modification of the resource

location.Description: The geo-location where the resource lives

principalId.Description: The principal id of connected cluster identity. This property will only be provided for a system assigned identity.

tenantId.Description: The tenant id associated with the connected cluster. This property will only be provided for a system assigned identity.

type.Description: The type of identity used for the connected cluster. The type 'SystemAssigned, includes a system created identity. The type 'None' means no identity is assigned to the connected cluster.

agentPublicKeyCertificate.Description: Base64 encoded public certificate used by the agent to do the initial handshake to the backend services in Azure.

kubernetesVersion.Description: The Kubernetes version of the connected cluster resource

totalNodeCount.Description: Number of nodes present in the connected cluster resource

totalCoreCount.Description: Number of CPU cores present in the connected cluster resource

agentVersion.Description: Version of the agent running on the connected cluster resource

provisioningState.Description: Provisioning state of the connected cluster resource.

distribution.Description: The Kubernetes distribution running on this connected cluster.

infrastructure.Description: The infrastructure on which the Kubernetes cluster represented by this connected cluster is running on.

managedIdentityCertificateExpirationTime.Description: Expiration time of the managed identity certificate

lastConnectivityTime.Description: Time representing the last instance when heart beat was received from the cluster

connectivityStatus.Description: Represents the connectivity status of the connected cluster.

privateLinkState.Description: Property which describes the state of private link on a connected cluster resource.

privateLinkScopeResourceId.Description: The resource id of the private link scope this connected cluster is assigned to, if any.

createdBy.Description: The identity that created the resource.

createdByType.Description: The type of identity that created the resource.

lastModifiedBy.Description: The identity that last modified the resource.

lastModifiedByType.Description: The type of identity that last modified the resource.

clientProxy.Description: Boolean value to indicate whether the request is for client side proxy or not

hybridConnectionConfig.Description: Contains the REP (rendezvous endpoint) and “Sender” access token.

expirationTime.Description: Timestamp when this token will be expired.
